Class CModifiedCustomerData

java.lang.Object
CModifiedCustomerData
public class CModifiedCustomerData
extends java.lang.Object
CModifiedCustomerData class represents modified customer data with fields for customer phone, contact name, and email address. It provides a constructor and getters/setters for these fields.

2023-12-14
Version:
